activities: My Custom IT provides web based Event Management software as service to its clients for the purpose of online e-commerce transactions. Our software allows our client’s customers to register for events and purchase merchandise on line. Our client’s collect data from their customers as part of the online transaction process. Our clients can customize the software to collect the data they need from their customers to complete the transaction. My Custom IT does not provide collected data to any third party accept those required to complete the transaction or as legally directed by our client.
